# Keep the Docker build context small + secret-free.
# Build context is the REPO ROOT for both images (pnpm workspace needs the lockfile,
# pnpm-workspace.yaml, and every package.json). Do NOT ignore src — the API runs
# TypeORM migrations against TypeScript source via ts-node at container start.

**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage

.git
.github
docs
infra

**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Never bake secrets into an image (but keep the example envs).
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/env-example-relational

.DS_Store
**/*.log
